src:
Nova pobeda Nine Stojanović
06 Nov 2019, 17:22 by Milos
Nina Stojanović izborila je plasman u drugo kolo WTA čelendžera u Šenženu, koji s eigra za nagradni fond od 100 hiljada dolara.
Najbolja srpska teniserka, inače postavljena za četvrtog nosioca na turniru u Kini, bila je bolja od Tajlanđanke Peangtarm Plipeuč sa 2:0, po setovima 6:1, 6:1, nakon 53 minuta igre.
Stojanovićeva, trenutno 86. teniserka na svetu, će se za plasman u četvrtfinale boriti sa donaćom predstavnicom Čang Liju.

POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
New victory for Nina Stojanovic
06 Nov 2019, 16:22 by Milos
Nina Stojanovic has won the second round of the WTA Welder in Shenzhen, which will play for the $ 100,000 prize pool.
The best Serbian tennis player, otherwise ranked fourth in the tournament in China, was better than Thailand's Peangtarm Plipeuc with 2: 0 in sets of 6: 1, 6: 1, after 53 minutes of play.
Stojanovic, currently the 86th tennis player in the world, will compete with donor representative Chang Li for the quarterfinals.
